55:\"<p>We recently released a security update to W3 Total Cache that addresses a vulnerability that can be exploited on misconfigured servers when database caching to disk is enabled. All users are encouraged to update.</p>\n<p>If you see the following error following the upgrade:<br />\n<code>Fatal error: Call to undefined function w3_is_dbcluster() in /path/to/wp-content/some-file.php</code></p>\n<p>This likely means that you&#8217;ve had us configure W3 Total Cache on your site already, and you were running a newer version of the plugin already. </p>\n<p>You&#8217;ll need to manually disable W3 Total Cache to restore access and <a href=\"http://www.w3-edge.com/contact/\">reach out</a> so we can get you sorted.</p>\n<div class=\"feedflare\">\n<a href=\"http://feeds.w3-edge.com/~ff/W3EDGE?a=roTCgklYEgQ:qMSvSpoLW84:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/W3EDGE?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.w3-edge.com/~ff/W3EDGE?a=roTCgklYEgQ:qMSvSpoLW84:D7DqB2pKExk\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/W3EDGE?i=roTCgklYEgQ:qMSvSpoLW84:D7DqB2pKExk\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.w3-edge.com/~ff/W3EDGE?a=roTCgklYEgQ:qMSvSpoLW84:F7zBnMyn0Lo\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/W3EDGE?i=roTCgklYEgQ:qMSvSpoLW84:F7zBnMyn0Lo\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.w3-edge.com/~ff/W3EDGE?a=roTCgklYEgQ:qMSvSpoLW84:qj6IDK7rITs\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/W3EDGE?d=qj6IDK7rITs\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.w3-edge.com/~ff/W3EDGE?a=roTCgklYEgQ:qMSvSpoLW84:gIN9vFwOqvQ\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/W3EDGE?i=roTCgklYEgQ:qMSvSpoLW84:gIN9vFwOqvQ\" border=\"0\"></img></a>\n</div><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/W3EDGE/~4/roTCgklYEgQ\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a: