INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (3512,5,'2013-02-11 14:04:18','2013-02-11 14:04:18','<h2>LATEST BATCH</h2>\r\n[custom-list post_type=\"teams\" taxonomy=\"session\" terms=\"spring-2013\" Spring 2013\" orderby=\"title\" order=\"asc\" ]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2>WHO WE ARE</h2>\r\nFlashpoint creates better startups, faster.  Our input is startup founders who care about their customers. Our output is startups with true market/product fit, reduced risks, lower costs, and a better chance of high quality success.   Flashpoint is the opposite of an incubator: instead of shielding startups from risk so they can create products, we expose them to customers and partners and help them shape themselves into companies with a valid business model.\r\n\r\nWhat’s unique about Flashpoint?  We teach Startup Engineering.  We teach founders how to clarify the thesis of their business, generate hypotheses to test it, conduct experiments, and leverage the results in order to mold the business to their customers.  Using and adapting insights from behavioral economics, decision theory, and \"immunity to change,\" we work with founders to systematically reduce the ambiguities, uncertainties, and inaccuracies surrounding their business model.  We get startups moving incredibly fast and we teach founders the process.\r\n<h2>WHO WE ARE LOOKING FOR</h2>\r\nWe need founders to be full-time committed to their startups and to have strong working relationships. The startup engineering work requires teams to have significant domain knowledge and to have relevant technical expertise ready to hand. We look for people who are demonstrably motivated to create scalable important businesses.\r\n\r\nWe like all startups, but especially technology startups. Atlanta is a great place for e-commerce, internet security, materials, consumer health, medical devices, computing, robotics, financial transactions, and logistics. With our connections to Georgia Tech and the Atlanta corporate community, we look for teams we think we may strongly advantage by providing access to resources in our networks.\r\n<h2>OUR PARTNERS</h2>\r\n[custom-list post_type=\"partners\" taxonomy=\"any\" terms=\"all_taxo\" orderby=\"menu_order\" order=\"asc\" showposts=\"0\" ]','Home','','publish','closed','open','','home','','','2013-03-07 18:43:56','2013-03-07 18:43:56','',0,'http://flashpoint.ei2.org/?page_id=3512',0,'page','',0);
