INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (3646,5,'2013-02-14 17:58:29','2013-02-14 17:58:29','William J. Hoffman Jr. (Chip) was the CEO of NeoMedia Technologies, Inc. (BB:NEOM) and CEO of Mobile Tag, Inc, the world’s leading provider of technology andservices for Mobile Operators, Handset manufactures, Advertisers, and Enterprises allowing camera phones to read and process 1D and 2D bar-codes.\r\n\r\nMr. Hoffman has two decades of global Executive and Operations Management experience in transaction-based technology for Telecom, Finance and Media. Experience includes Team Creation and Leadership, Sales and Marketing, Corporate Turn-around and Financial Restructuring, Operations, Mobility and Wireless Technology, SaaS, Cloud-computing, Media, Telecommunications, and Process-based Program Management.\r\n\r\nHis expertise spans both public and private companies, Fortune 500s and start-ups, and professional services businesses which provide him with broad, “real-world tested” experience. His perspective on the evolving Technology, Digital Media, Telecom Infrastructure and Internet Security world is unique. He has worked closely with Google, mBlox, AT&amp;T, Sprint, Verizon, Publicis, Interpublic Group, WPP, and others on all aspects of the business including infrastructure, logistics, sourcing, telecommunications technology, and interactive advertising.\r\n\r\n10(+) years in both private and public company \"C-level\" roles, he is able to recruit, develop and lead high-performance teams on a global basis by managing Business Processes cross-functionally. Mr. Hoffman\'s ability to achieve goals and results is due to his focus to set, manage, measure, and analyze business performance through information. He is also known as a “Highly Effective Communicator”.\r\n\r\nDomiciled throughout the continental US and 6+ years abroad, Mr. Hoffman also served for the US Intelligence community and obtained the highest-level security clearance and compartmentalization.','William J. \'Chip\' Hoffman','','publish','closed','closed','','william-j-chip-hoffman','','','2013-02-14 17:58:29','2013-02-14 17:58:29','',0,'http://flashpoint.ei2.org/?post_type=mentors&#038;p=3646',0,'mentors','',0);
