INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (4018,5,'2013-02-19 15:20:58','2013-02-19 15:20:58','<strong>Xconomy (1/19/12):</strong> A flotilla of fifteen startups from Atlanta presented their ideas in New York on Wednesday for a demo day at the offices of Union Square Ventures. Merrick Furst, director of the Flashpoint accelerator at the Georgia Institute of Technology, said the program helps entrepreneurs develop their concepts beyond their startup phase. “They are trying to figure out what the business opportunity is,” he said... <a href=\"http://www.xconomy.com/new-york/2012/01/19/georgia-startups-have-new-york-on-their-minds-at-flashpoint-demo-day/?single_page=true\">Read more &raquo;</a>','Georgia Startups Have New York on Their Minds at Flashpoint Demo Day','','inherit','closed','open','','774-revision-2','','','2013-02-19 15:20:58','2013-02-19 15:20:58','',774,'http://flashpoint.ei2.org/774-revision-2/',0,'revision','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (4019,5,'2013-02-19 06:53:01','2013-02-19 06:53:01','<strong>Force of Good (1/12/12):</strong> Earlier this week <a href=\"http://flashpoint.gatech.edu/\" target=\"_self\">Flashpoint</a>, Georgia Tech\'s new startup accelerator, held it first ever demo day. While really a bit more of a pitch day, I only saw one demo, the teams did a great job. Locally David Cummings has a <a href=\"http://davidcummings.org/2012/01/10/flashpoint-demo-day-startups-january-2012/\" target=\"_self\">nice summary of the companies that pitched</a>and TechCrunch even <a href=\"http://techcrunch.com/2012/01/10/georgia-techs-flashpoint-accelerator-graduates-its-first-class-of-startups/\" target=\"_self\">covered the event</a>.\r\n\r\nWhile in many respects it is to soon to tell, the capstone of the program begs the question \"is Flashpoint a success?\" The early answer is yes... <a href=\"http://blog.weatherby.net/2012/01/flashpoint-winning.html\">Read more &raquo;</a>','Flashpoint: Winning','','inherit','closed','open','','760-revision-2','','','2013-02-19 06:53:01','2013-02-19 06:53:01','',760,'http://flashpoint.ei2.org/760-revision-2/',0,'revision','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (4020,5,'2013-02-19 15:21:45','2013-02-19 15:21:45','<strong>TechDrawl (1/11/12):</strong> Congratulations to all involved in the first iteration of the <a href=\"http://flashpoint.gatech.edu/\" target=\"_blank\">Flashpoint</a> program at Georgia Tech.  A very carefully curated group of startups was well coached and brought to the stage on Tuesday January 10 in one of the most flawless venues and formats I’ve seen.\r\n\r\nOpportunity is knocking for Atlanta’s tech angels.  From personally making the rounds in Atlanta, Austin &amp; New York, I can confidently say that the presenters at Flashpoint Demo Day brought everything one could ask in a tech startup...now will investors out there respond in kind?... <a href=\"http://techdrawl.com/flashpoint-has-startups-needs-angels\">Read more »</a>','Flashpoint has Startups: Needs Angels','','inherit','closed','open','','757-revision-3','','','2013-02-19 15:21:45','2013-02-19 15:21:45','',757,'http://flashpoint.ei2.org/757-revision-3/',0,'revision','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (4021,5,'2013-02-19 15:22:27','2013-02-19 15:22:27','<strong>TechCrunch (1/10/12):</strong> <a href=\"http://flashpoint.gatech.edu/\" target=\"_blank\">Flashpoint</a>, a startup accelerator program based at Georgia Tech in Atlanta, Georgia, just had its first Demo Day at the Georgia Tech Research Institute. The newly launched incubator follows the typical format for programs like this, offering seed funding, <a href=\"http://flashpoint.gatech.edu/mentors/\">mentorship</a>, support, shared workspace and more, in return for a 6% share of the startup... <a href=\"http://techcrunch.com/2012/01/10/georgia-techs-flashpoint-accelerator-graduates-its-first-class-of-startups/\">Read more »</a>','Georgia Tech’s Flashpoint Accelerator Graduates Its First Class Of Startups','','inherit','closed','open','','755-revision-3','','','2013-02-19 15:22:27','2013-02-19 15:22:27','',755,'http://flashpoint.ei2.org/755-revision-3/',0,'revision','',0);
