INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (4050,5,'2013-02-19 16:47:29','2013-02-19 16:47:29','<strong><img class=\"alignright\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://6.mshcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/FlashpointDemoDay.jpg\" width=\"358\" height=\"221\" />Mashable (1/27/12): </strong>A gathering of entrepreneurs in the Bay Area on Thursday offered a window into how ambitious techies’ visions become reality. It started with a presentation from a go-getter named Adam Ghetti.\r\n\r\nDressed casually in a dark tee-shirt, Ghetti stepped to the front a conference room at the <a href=\"http://mashable.com/follow/topics/silicon-valley/\">Silicon Valley</a> venture capital firm Andreessen Horowitz on Thursday afternoon. He launched into an intense, rapid-fire pitch and test drive of his cloud security <a href=\"http://mashable.com/startups/\">startup</a> Social Fortress.\r\n\r\nAfter Ghetti finished, 14 more entrepreneurs repeated the process, describing the basics of their businesses. They hoped to spark interest — and investment... <a href=\"http://mashable.com/2012/01/27/flashpoint-demo-entrepreneurs/\">Read more »</a>','Flashpoint Demo Day a Glimpse of How Entrepreneurs’ Dreams Come True','','inherit','closed','open','','777-revision-6','','','2013-02-19 16:47:29','2013-02-19 16:47:29','',777,'http://flashpoint.ei2.org/777-revision-6/',0,'revision','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (4051,5,'2013-02-19 16:47:35','2013-02-19 16:47:35','<strong>Xconomy (1/19/12):</strong> A flotilla of fifteen startups from Atlanta presented their ideas in New York on Wednesday for a demo day at the offices of Union Square Ventures. Merrick Furst, director of the Flashpoint accelerator at the Georgia Institute of Technology, said the program helps entrepreneurs develop their concepts beyond their startup phase. “They are trying to figure out what the business opportunity is,” he said... <a href=\"http://www.xconomy.com/new-york/2012/01/19/georgia-startups-have-new-york-on-their-minds-at-flashpoint-demo-day/?single_page=true\">Read more &raquo;</a>','Georgia Startups Have New York on Their Minds at Flashpoint Demo Day','','inherit','closed','open','','774-revision-4','','','2013-02-19 16:47:35','2013-02-19 16:47:35','',774,'http://flashpoint.ei2.org/774-revision-4/',0,'revision','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (4052,5,'2013-02-19 16:47:41','2013-02-19 16:47:41','<strong>Force of Good (1/12/12):</strong> Earlier this week <a href=\"http://flashpoint.gatech.edu/\" target=\"_self\">Flashpoint</a>, Georgia Tech\'s new startup accelerator, held it first ever demo day. While really a bit more of a pitch day, I only saw one demo, the teams did a great job. Locally David Cummings has a <a href=\"http://davidcummings.org/2012/01/10/flashpoint-demo-day-startups-january-2012/\" target=\"_self\">nice summary of the companies that pitched</a>and TechCrunch even <a href=\"http://techcrunch.com/2012/01/10/georgia-techs-flashpoint-accelerator-graduates-its-first-class-of-startups/\" target=\"_self\">covered the event</a>.\r\n\r\nWhile in many respects it is to soon to tell, the capstone of the program begs the question \"is Flashpoint a success?\" The early answer is yes... <a href=\"http://blog.weatherby.net/2012/01/flashpoint-winning.html\">Read more &raquo;</a>','Flashpoint: Winning','','inherit','closed','open','','760-revision-4','','','2013-02-19 16:47:41','2013-02-19 16:47:41','',760,'http://flashpoint.ei2.org/760-revision-4/',0,'revision','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (4053,5,'2013-02-19 16:47:46','2013-02-19 16:47:46','<strong>TechDrawl (1/11/12):</strong> Congratulations to all involved in the first iteration of the <a href=\"http://flashpoint.gatech.edu/\" target=\"_blank\">Flashpoint</a> program at Georgia Tech.  A very carefully curated group of startups was well coached and brought to the stage on Tuesday January 10 in one of the most flawless venues and formats I’ve seen.\r\n\r\nOpportunity is knocking for Atlanta’s tech angels.  From personally making the rounds in Atlanta, Austin &amp; New York, I can confidently say that the presenters at Flashpoint Demo Day brought everything one could ask in a tech startup...now will investors out there respond in kind?... <a href=\"http://techdrawl.com/flashpoint-has-startups-needs-angels\">Read more »</a>','Flashpoint has Startups: Needs Angels','','inherit','closed','open','','757-revision-5','','','2013-02-19 16:47:46','2013-02-19 16:47:46','',757,'http://flashpoint.ei2.org/757-revision-5/',0,'revision','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (4054,5,'2013-02-19 16:47:52','2013-02-19 16:47:52','<strong>TechCrunch (1/10/12):</strong> <a href=\"http://flashpoint.gatech.edu/\" target=\"_blank\">Flashpoint</a>, a startup accelerator program based at Georgia Tech in Atlanta, Georgia, just had its first Demo Day at the Georgia Tech Research Institute. The newly launched incubator follows the typical format for programs like this, offering seed funding, <a href=\"http://flashpoint.gatech.edu/mentors/\">mentorship</a>, support, shared workspace and more, in return for a 6% share of the startup... <a href=\"http://techcrunch.com/2012/01/10/georgia-techs-flashpoint-accelerator-graduates-its-first-class-of-startups/\">Read more »</a>','Georgia Tech’s Flashpoint Accelerator Graduates Its First Class Of Startups','','inherit','closed','open','','755-revision-5','','','2013-02-19 16:47:52','2013-02-19 16:47:52','',755,'http://flashpoint.ei2.org/755-revision-5/',0,'revision','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (4055,5,'2013-02-19 16:47:58','2013-02-19 16:47:58','<strong>Atlanta Business Chronicle (1/9/12): </strong>It\'s demo time!\r\n\r\nOn Tuesday, the inaugural class of <a href=\"http://flashpoint.gatech.edu/\" target=\"_blank\">Flashpoint</a>will pitch their startups to about 250, half of whom will be investors.\r\n\r\nFlashpoint, <a href=\"http://www.bizjournals.com/atlanta/blog/atlantech/2011/08/accelerator-flashpoint-launches-first.html\" target=\"_blank\">launched last year</a> by Georgia Tech and backed by a $1 million fund, hopes to lure promising technology, medical device and biotech startups to metro Atlanta... <a href=\"http://www.bizjournals.com/atlanta/blog/atlantech/2012/01/flashpoint-startups-ready-for-demo-day.html\">Read more »</a>','Flashpoint startups ready for demo day','','inherit','closed','open','','753-revision-5','','','2013-02-19 16:47:58','2013-02-19 16:47:58','',753,'http://flashpoint.ei2.org/753-revision-5/',0,'revision','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (4056,5,'2013-02-19 16:48:08','2013-02-19 16:48:08','<strong>10,000 Startup Hours (1/10/12):</strong> Today I had a great time watching 15 startups in the <a href=\"http://flashpoint.gatech.edu/\">Flashpoint</a> cohort give six minute pitches at the Georgia Tech Research Institute. The teams have been working together since September 2011 and have made amazing progress.\r\n\r\nHere are notes from the 15 startups... <a href=\"http://davidcummings.org/2012/01/10/flashpoint-demo-day-startups-january-2012/\">Read more »</a>','Flashpoint Demo Day Startups January 2012','','inherit','closed','open','','751-revision-5','','','2013-02-19 16:48:08','2013-02-19 16:48:08','',751,'http://flashpoint.ei2.org/751-revision-5/',0,'revision','',0);
