"isRequired\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"size\";s:6:\"medium\";s:4:\"type\";s:8:\"textarea\";s:5:\"label\";s:203:\"What job, or customer need, do you hope your startup addresses? How do you know about this need?  How did you choose this problem to solve?  What about this problem makes it attractive to you to work on?\";}i:5;a:5:{s:2:\"id\";s:1:\"9\";s:10:\"isRequired\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"size\";s:6:\"medium\";s:4:\"type\";s:8:\"textarea\";s:5:\"label\";s:82:\"What do you know about this problem or technology that others don’t know or get?\";}i:6;a:5:{s:2:\"id\";s:2:\"10\";s:10:\"isRequired\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"size\";s:6:\"medium\";s:4:\"type\";s:8:\"textarea\";s:5:\"label\";s:138:\"How long have you been working on this problem? Do you have current customers? Do you have current revenue? If so, how fast is it growing?\";}i:7;a:5:{s:2:\"id\";s:2:\"44\";s:4:\"size\";s:6:\"medium\";s:4:\"type\";s:8:\"textarea\";s:11:\"description\";s:22:\"Please provide URL(s).\";s:5:\"label\";s:65:\"Is there anything we can look at online?  An app, website, etc?  \";}i:8;a:5:{s:2:\"id\";s:2:\"12\";s:10:\"isRequired\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"size\";s:6:\"medium\";s:4:\"type\";s:8:\"textarea\";s:5:\"label\";s:188:\"Identify your target market or domain of market expertise.  What domain experience and knowledge do you believe will be important for a company to have to operate efficiently in this area.\";}i:9;a:5:{s:2:\"id\";s:2:\"14\";s:10:\"isRequired\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"size\";s:6:\"medium\";s:4:\"type\";s:8:\"textarea\";s:5:\"label\";s:199:\"Describe your expertise in this domain. How did you arrive at it, what validates your view of it?  What additional knowledge do you think you need to acquire, and how you might go about getting that?\";}i:10;a:5:{s:2:\"id\";s:2:\"15\";s:10:\"isRequired\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"size\";s:6:\"medium\";s:4:\"type\";s:8:\"textarea\";s:5:\"label\";s:109:\"Do you have evidence that there is a true need for your product or service? How did you obtain this evidence?\";}i:11;a:5:{s:2:\"id\";s:2:\"16\";s:10:\"isRequired\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"size\";s:6:\"medium\";s:4:\"type\";s:8:\"textarea\";s:5:\"label\";s:165:\"Describe your team’s experience in gathering customer feedback on proposed products or solutions. What role has each team member played in gathering this feedback?\";}i:12;a:5:{s:2:\"id\";s:2:\"19\";s:10:\"isRequired\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"size\";s:6:\"medium\";s:4:\"type\";s:8:\"textarea\";s:5:\"label\";s:189:\"How big a business do you think this can become? What total addressable market and market share assumptions you are making about this business? Explain how you arrived at these assumptions.\";}i:13;a:5:{s:2:\"id\";s:2:\"20\";s:10:\"isRequired\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"size\";s:6:\"medium\";s:4:\"type\";s:8:\"textarea\";s:5:\"label\";s:60:\"Do you have a plan to acquire customers?  If so, what is it?\";}i:14;a:5:{s:2:\"id\";s:2:\"21\";s:10:\"isRequired\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"size\";s:6:\"medium\";s:4:\"type\";s:8:\"textarea\";s:5:\"label\";s:26:\"Describe your competition.\";}i:15;a:5:{s:2:\"id\";s:2:\"24\";s:10:\"isRequired\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"size\";s:6:\"medium\";s:4:\"type\";s:8:\"textarea\";s:5:\"label\";s:149:\"How did the founders meet? What role will each founder play? How long have the founders known each other? Have any of the founders not met in person?\";}i:16;a:5:{s:2:\"id\";s:2:\"25\";s:10:\"isRequired\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"size\";s:6:\"medium\";s:4:\"type\";s:8:\"textarea\";s:5:\"label\";s:55:\"How long has this team worked together on this company?\";}i:17;a:5:{s:2:\"id\";s:2:\"26\";s:10:\"isRequired\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"size\";s:6:\"medium\";s:4:\"type\";s:8:\"textarea\";s:5:\"label\";s:158:\"Have any team members worked together in the past? If so, please describe how long, what roles each team member had, what projects and progress you achieved. \";}i:18;a:5:{s:2:\"id\";s:2:\"27\";s:10:\"isRequired\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"size\";s:6:\"medium\";s:4:\"type\";s:8:\"textarea\";s:5:\"label\";s:97:\"Identify the technical skills you believe will be important for your company in its early stages.\";}i:19;a:5:{s:2:\"id\";s:2:\"28\";s:10:\"isRequired\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"size\";s:6:\"medium\";s:4:\"type\";s:8:\"textarea\";s:5:\"label\";s:300:\"Describe your team’s technical skills, relevant to this opportunity. Please include years of relevant experience and describe why the experience was relevant. If there are technical skills you believe you need at this stage of the company, but do not possess, how do you plan to solve this problem?\";}i:20;a:5:{s:2:\"id\";s:2:\"29\";s:10:\"isRequired\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"size\";s:6:\"medium\";s:4:\"type\";s:8:\"textarea\";s:5:\"label\";s:90:\"If you had to define your next hire, what would it be?  How will you obtain this resource?\";}i:21;a:5:{s:2:\"id\";s:2:\"30\";s:10:\"isRequired\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"size\";s:6:\"medium\";s:4:\"type\";s:8:\"textarea\";s:5:\"label\";s:119:\"Describe the experience your team has had in acquiring talent - how many people, what skills and over what time period.\";}i:22;a:5:{s:2:\"id\";s:2:\"33\";s:10:\"isRequired\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"size\";s:6:\"medium\";s:4:\"type\";s:8:\"textarea\";s:5:\"label\";s:110:\"Describe any potential conflicts you are aware of with respect to intellectual property or non-compete issues?\";}i:23;a:6:{s:2:\"id\";s:2:\"34\";s:10:\"isRequired\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"size\";s:6:\"medium\";s:4:\"type\";s:8:\"textarea\";s:11:\"description\";s:34:\"Not required.  We\'re just curious.\";s:5:\"label\";s:79:\"Do you have any relationship with GT (faculty, current student, graduate, etc)?\";}i:24;a:6:{s:2:\"id\";s:2:\"35\";s:10:\"isRequired\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"size\";s:6:\"medium\";s:4:\"type\";s:8:\"textarea\";s:11:\"description\";s:22:\"If so, please explain.\";s:5:\"label\";s:66:\"Do you need to license any intellectual property to be successful?\";}i:25;a:5:{s:2:\"id\";s:2:\"36\";s:10:\"isRequired\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"size\";s:6:\"medium\";s:4:\"type\";s:8:\"textarea\";s:5:\"label\";s:30:\"Where does your team live now?\";}i:26;a:5:{s:2:\"id\";s:2:\"37\";s:10:\"isRequired\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"size\";s:6:\"medium\";s:4:\"type\";s:8:\"textarea\";s:5:\"label\";s:39:\"After Flashpoint - where will you live?\";}i:27;a:5:{s:2:\"id\";s:2:\"38\";s:10:\"isRequired\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"size\";s:6:\"medium\";s:4:\"type\";s:8:\"textarea\";s:5:\"label\";s:175:\"Is your company incorporated? How many shareholders does your company have? Have you raised any money? If so, at what valuation? If not, how have you been funding the company?\";}i:28;a:5:{s:2:\"id\";s:2:\"39\";s:10:\"isRequired\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"size\";s:6:\"medium\";s:4:\"type\";s:8:\"textarea\";s:5:\"label\";s:105:\"Describe any significant outside commitments any of the founders will have during the four month program?\";}i:29;a:5:{s:2:\"id\";s:2:\"40\";s:10:\"isRequired\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"size\";s:6:\"medium\";s:4:\"type\";s:8:\"textarea\";s:5:\"label\";s:93:\"Describe any significant outside commitments any of the founders will have after the program?\";}i:30;a:5:{s:2:\"id\";s:2:\"41\";s:10:\"isRequired\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"size\";s:6:\"medium\";s:4:\"type\";s:8:\"textarea\";s:5:\"label\";s:125:\"Are there any other employees besides founders? If so, please describe their role(s) and the founder’s commitments to them.\";}i:31;a:5:{s:2:\"id\";s:2:\"42\";s:10:\"isRequired\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"size\";s:6:\"medium\";s:4:\"type\";s:8:\"textarea\";s:5:\"label\";s:90:\"Why are you applying to Flashpoint and what would you want Flashpoint to help you achieve?\";}}s:12:\"notification\";a:5:{s:2:\"to\";s:22:\"merrickfurst@gmail.com\";s:7:\"subject\";s:32:\"New submission from {form_title}\";s:7:\"message\";s:12:\"{all_fields}\";s:4:\"from\";s:13:\"{admin_email}\";s:8:\"fromName\";s:21:\"Merrick at Flashpoint\";}s:11:\"description\";s:61:\"Interviews in progress. You may still apply for our waitlist.\";s:20:\"descriptionPlacement\";s:5:\"above\";s:14:\"enableHoneypot\";s:1:\"1\";s:2:\"id\";i:3;}',NULL);
